Package: ftWrapper
Type: Package
Title: Provide Wrappers for Several Flextable Operations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hayden Atchley
Maintainer: Hayden Atchley <atchley.sha@protonmail.com>
Description: A collection of wrappers for operations in the 'flextable' package.
   This is tailored to my specific use cases, which include in particular
   displaying statistical analysis results. However, several other wrappers may
   be included, and the package contents are likely to change over time.
